    "description_long": "This is a white ceramic cup with a polygonal, bright green handle attached to one side. The cup features a detailed character graphic on one side, depicting a humanoid figure in armor, and a large, stylized logo with orange and black segments on the opposite side. The rim and base of the cup are accented with a dark gray band, providing a subtle contrast to the main white body. The handle is thick and angular, making it easy to grip. The cup's interior is plain and appears to be spacious, suitable for holding hot or cold beverages.",
